message:
Meeting in Camdenton held to bring awareness to human trafficking
"It's so hard to track down who the traffickers are, because we have very long and complicated supply chains"

data.description: Being in the heart of the state, the Lake of the Ozarks Stop Human Trafficking Coalition wants the community to know and be aware that it could be happening right here at home.
data.title: Meeting in Camdenton held to bring awareness to human trafficking
